plot: Comedians get competitive as devious Greg Davies sets them absurd challenges. Identifying pie contents and making a film backwards are on the agenda here.

Nobly assisted by Alex Horne, Taskmaster Greg Davies commands his captive band of comedians (Roisin Conaty, Tim Key, Romesh Ranganathan, Frank Skinner and Josh Widdicombe) to identify the contents of a table full of mystery pies, make a film backwards, and high five a fifty-five year old.
